::Autofire::

Autofire walks into the room, looking at Adrx with a questionary look as he 
sees Waspinator. He had been in the hangars, working on various equipment.

Autofire walks toward Adrax, his armor stained with oil and various other 
machine fluids.

"What's going on?" he asks, indicating Waspinator.
